column2: "What? There's a ton of them here, too! What are we gonna do?"
"It's more interesting if there are challenges along the way, right? Shut up and get used to it."
"Well, it's about the right time, but I guess she's late."
"Sorry, rookies. I called for backup, but she's still not here yet."
"Hey there, Zeno! Don't go giving the new recruits the wrong impression of me."
"It's your fault for being late. But more importantly, how's the situation looking?"
"Still not good. With this much Darker activity, we won't be able to make an extraction."
"I see. So, basically, we can get out of here once we've taken care of these Darkers."
"No need. This rookie here is pretty good. Maybe even stronger than you!"

"Okay, rookies, this is the last of
them. Let's take care of these guys and call it a day."
